---
import GlobalFooter from '../components/GlobalFooter.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <title>AI CMO Advisor Pricing | Treetop Growth Strategy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Start at $99 for a one-time competitive report, then climb only as far as you need: Monitor ($249/mo), Guided ($999/mo), Embedded ($2,500/mo), or a custom Enterprise engagement. Each step does more of the work for you." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/pricing" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/pricing" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="AI CMO Advisor Pricing | Treetop" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Start at $99. Climb only as far as you need: Monitor, Guided, Embedded, Enterprise. Each step does more of the work for you." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/og-default.png" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Treetop Growth Strategy" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="AI CMO Advisor Pricing | Treetop" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Start at $99, climb only as far as you need. Five steps, each doing more of the work for you." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: #050D05; color: #F0FFF0; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 50; background: rgba(5,13,5,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2.5rem; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .nav-logo { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #F0FFF0; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(240,255,240,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link:hover { color: #F0FFF0; }
    .btn-p { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: #00C853; color: #050D05; padding: 0.75rem 1.4rem; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; }
    .btn-p:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
    .btn-g { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: transparent; color: #F0FFF0; padding: 0.75rem 1.4rem; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; white-space: nowrap; }
    .btn-g:hover { border-color: rgba(0,200,83,0.4); background: rgba(0,200,83,0.05); }
    .hero { padding: 8rem 2.5rem 3rem; }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
    .lbl { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #00C853; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: block; }
    .hero-h { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.08; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .hero-h em { color: #00C853; font-style: italic; }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 680px; }
    section { padding: 4.5rem 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .sec-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .h2 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 400; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.15; }
    .body { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    /* Stairstep */
    .stair { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
    .rung { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 30px 1fr auto auto; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center; background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; border-left: 3px solid #1A3A1A; padding: 1.6rem 1.9rem; transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
    .rung:hover { background: #0f200f; border-left-color: rgba(0,200,83,0.5); }
    .rung.featured { border-color: rgba(0,200,83,0.35); border-left-color: #00C853; }
    .rung-num { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-style: italic; color: rgba(0,200,83,0.35); line-height: 1; }
    .rung.featured .rung-num { color: #00C853; }
    .rung-name { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .rung-name .tag { display: inline-block; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0,200,83,0.12); color: #00C853; padding: 2px 7px; margin-left: 0.6rem; vertical-align: middle; }
    .rung-best { font-size: 0.86rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.5; }
    .rung-best strong { color: #C0D8C0; font-weight: 500; }
    .rung-climb { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #4A6A4A; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.35rem; }
    .rung-price { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.9rem; color: #F0FFF0; line-height: 1; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }
    .rung-price small { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.72rem; color: #4A6A4A; font-weight: 400; }
    .rung-price em { color: #00C853; font-style: normal; }

    /* Comparison table */
    .table-wrap { margin-top: 2rem; overflow-x: auto; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    table.cmp { width: 100%; min-width: 820px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    table.cmp th, table.cmp td { padding: 0.9rem 1rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; vertical-align: top; }
    table.cmp thead th { background: #0A1A0A; color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    table.cmp thead th .th-price { display: block; font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1rem; color: #00C853; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 0.15rem; }
    table.cmp tbody th { font-weight: 400; color: #C0D8C0; background: #070F07; }
    table.cmp td { color: #8FAF8F; text-align: center; }
    table.cmp td:first-of-type, table.cmp tbody th { text-align: left; }
    table.cmp .yes { color: #00C853; font-weight: 600; }
    table.cmp .no { color: #2A4A2A; }
    table.cmp tbody tr:hover td, table.cmp tbody tr:hover th { background: rgba(0,200,83,0.03); }
    table.cmp .row-price th { font-weight: 600; color: #F0FFF0; }
    table.cmp .row-price td { color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 500; }

    .faq { background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .faq h3 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .faq p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.7; }
    .faq a { color: #00C853; text-decoration: none; }
    .cta-box { background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,83,0.2); padding: 3rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .cta-text { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #F0FFF0; }
    .cta-sub { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #8FAF8F; margin-top: 0.5rem; max-width: 560px; }

    @media(max-width: 820px) {
      section { padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; }
      .hero { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 2.5rem; }
      .hide-mob { display: none !important; }
      .rung { grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 0.75rem 1rem; padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem; }
      .rung-num { display: none; }
      .rung-price { font-size: 1.6rem; text-align: right; }
      .rung-cta { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
      .rung-cta .btn-p, .rung-cta .btn-g { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Treetop</a>
    <div class="hide-mob" style="display:flex;gap:2rem;align-items:center;">
      <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="nav-link">AI CMO Advisor</a>
      <a href="/resources" class="nav-link">Resources</a>
      <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="btn-p" style="padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.78rem;">Get your report &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="lbl">Pricing</span>
    <h1 class="hero-h">Start at $99. <em>Climb only as far as you need.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Five steps, and each one does more of the work for you. Begin with a one-time $99 diagnosis. If you want it kept current, someone on call, or a hand actually doing the work, the next step is right there. No discovery call required to start, and no step locks you into the next.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STAIRSTEP -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">The ladder</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Diagnose. Monitor. Guide. Embed. Transform.</h2>
    <p class="body">The axis is simple: the higher you climb, the more of the work we take off your plate. Most people start at the bottom and never need to leave. Some climb one step. A few want the whole thing run for them.</p>

    <div class="stair">

      <div class="rung">
        <div class="rung-num">01</div>
        <div>
          <div class="rung-name">Starter Report</div>
          <div class="rung-best"><strong>Best for:</strong> seeing exactly where you stand, once. Live competitive data, a keyword gap, and a 90-day roadmap in your inbox same day.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rung-price"><em>$99</em><br/><small>one-time</small></div>
        <div class="rung-cta"><a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="btn-p">Get the report &rarr;</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="rung">
        <div class="rung-num">02</div>
        <div>
          <div class="rung-name">Monitor</div>
          <div class="rung-best"><strong>Best for:</strong> staying current without hiring. The report, refreshed every month, with a what-changed memo and one priority question answered.</div>
          <div class="rung-climb">Climb here when one snapshot isn't enough and you want it kept fresh.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rung-price"><em>$249</em><br/><small>/ month</small></div>
        <div class="rung-cta"><a href="/ai-cmo-advisor/upgrade?tier=monitor" class="btn-g">Start Monitor &rarr;</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="rung featured">
        <div class="rung-num">03</div>
        <div>
          <div class="rung-name">Guided <span class="tag">Most popular</span></div>
          <div class="rung-best"><strong>Best for:</strong> a plan plus a strategist on call. Everything in Monitor, a monthly working call, up to 6 competitors, and we draft or review your priority assets.</div>
          <div class="rung-climb">Climb here when you want to talk it through and have us shape the work.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rung-price"><em>$999</em><br/><small>/ month</small></div>
        <div class="rung-cta"><a href="/ai-cmo-advisor/upgrade?tier=guided" class="btn-p">Start Guided &rarr;</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="rung">
        <div class="rung-num">04</div>
        <div>
          <div class="rung-name">Embedded</div>
          <div class="rung-best"><strong>Best for:</strong> a part-time CMO who does the work with you. Biweekly calls, we produce the deliverables, and execution gets tracked, not just recommended.</div>
          <div class="rung-climb">Climb here when you need execution, not just direction.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rung-price"><em>$2,500</em><br/><small>/ month</small></div>
        <div class="rung-cta"><a href="/ai-cmo-advisor/upgrade?tier=embedded" class="btn-g">Start Embedded &rarr;</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="rung">
        <div class="rung-num">05</div>
        <div>
          <div class="rung-name">Enterprise</div>
          <div class="rung-best"><strong>Best for:</strong> rebuilding the whole revenue motion around AI. Full fractional leadership, team enablement, systems build, and board-ready reporting.</div>
          <div class="rung-climb">Climb here when it's a team-wide transformation, not a marketing task.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rung-price"><em>Custom</em><br/><small>let's scope it</small></div>
        <div class="rung-cta"><a href="https://calendar.app.google/GS5H5y8U3PrN8u4A8" class="btn-g">Book a call &rarr;</a></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">Compare</span>
    <h2 class="h2">What you get at each step.</h2>
    <p class="body">Everything below a tier is included in it. Scroll to compare across all five.</p>

    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table class="cmp">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>&nbsp;</th>
            <th>Starter<span class="th-price">$99</span></th>
            <th>Monitor<span class="th-price">$249/mo</span></th>
            <th>Guided<span class="th-price">$999/mo</span></th>
            <th>Embedded<span class="th-price">$2,500/mo</span></th>
            <th>Enterprise<span class="th-price">Custom</span></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th>Live competitive analysis</th>
            <td>Once</td><td>Monthly</td><td>Monthly</td><td>Monthly</td><td>Continuous</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Competitors tracked</th>
            <td>3</td><td>3</td><td>6</td><td>6+</td><td>Custom</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>90-day roadmap</th>
            <td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>What-changed memo</th>
            <td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Priority question answered</th>
            <td class="no">&middot;</td><td>1 / mo</td><td>Async</td><td>Direct</td><td>Continuous</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Monthly working call</th>
            <td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td>45 min</td><td>Biweekly</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>We draft / review your assets</th>
            <td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td>We produce them</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Hands-on execution</th>
            <td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>GTM build + team enablement</th>
            <td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="no">&middot;</td><td class="yes">&#10003;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="row-price">
            <th>Price</th>
            <td>$99 once</td><td>$249/mo</td><td>$999/mo</td><td>$2,500/mo</td><td>Custom</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">FAQ</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Common questions</h2>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>Do I have to start at the bottom?</h3>
      <p>No. Most people start with the $99 Starter Report because it's the lowest-risk way to see the thinking, but you can begin at any step. The ladder is there so you climb only when you actually need more, not because you were funneled into it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What's the real difference between the tiers?</h3>
      <p>How much of the work we do. Starter is a one-time diagnosis. Monitor keeps that diagnosis current. Guided adds a strategist you can talk to and who shapes your assets. Embedded is a part-time CMO who produces the work with you. Enterprise rebuilds the whole revenue motion. The data and the roadmap run through all of them; what changes is who does the doing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>Can I move up or down later?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Upgrade when you want more, cancel or step down when you want less. Subscriptions cancel any time from your Stripe customer portal, no calls and no notice period.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What data does the analysis use?</h3>
      <p>Live Ahrefs API data pulled at the time of each report: domain rating, organic keyword count, estimated monthly traffic, and the top traffic-driving keywords for you and your competitors. Plus the intake answers you provide about your business, goals, and budget.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>How fast does the report arrive?</h3>
      <p>Usually within a few hours, the same day in almost every case. We pull the data, run the analysis, and review it before it goes out. Always within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>When does Enterprise make sense over Embedded?</h3>
      <p>Embedded is a part-time CMO focused on your marketing motion at a flat $2,500 a month. Enterprise is for a team-wide, AI-native rebuild of the whole revenue system: it's custom-scoped, always a flat monthly fee, and starts with a call. Most Enterprise clients spend time on a lower rung first so both sides know the fit before scoping anything bigger.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <div class="cta-text">Start with the $99 report.</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">See exactly where you stand against your competitors, with a 90-day roadmap, in your inbox same day. Climb from there only if it's working.</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="btn-p" style="padding:0.9rem 1.75rem;font-size:0.85rem;">Get the report &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<GlobalFooter />

</body>
</html>
